  <title>Sorting some result list by the ids of another list</title>
  <description />
  <content>&lt;p&gt;Imagine we have the following list of ids of some kind of objects and a mapping of some of the ids to some values (also int’s here):&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;div style="border-bottom: silver 1px solid; text-align: left; border-left: silver 1px solid; padding-bottom: 4px; line-height: 12pt; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding-left: 4px; width: 97.5%; padding-right: 4px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; max-height: 200px; font-size: 8pt; overflow: auto; border-top: silver 1px solid; cursor: text; border-right: silver 1px solid; padding-top: 4px" id="codeSnippetWrapper"&gt;   &lt;div style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px" id="codeSnippet"&gt;     &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: white; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum1"&gt;   1:&lt;/span&gt; var ids = &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; List&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; { 6, 2, 5, 3, 7 };&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;

    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum2"&gt;   2:&lt;/span&gt; var valueMap = &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; List&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;[]&amp;gt; { &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt;[] { 5, 15 }, &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt;[] { 2, 12 }, &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt;[] { 3, 13 } };&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now, if we want to return the results a.k.a. the valueMap in the same order we have the ids, we can use the LINQ extension method &lt;font face="Courier New"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.Join()&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style="border-bottom: silver 1px solid; text-align: left; border-left: silver 1px solid; padding-bottom: 4px; line-height: 12pt; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding-left: 4px; width: 97.5%; padding-right: 4px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; max-height: 200px; font-size: 8pt; overflow: auto; border-top: silver 1px solid; cursor: text; border-right: silver 1px solid; padding-top: 4px" id="codeSnippetWrapper"&gt;
  &lt;div style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px" id="codeSnippet"&gt;
    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: white; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum1"&gt;   1:&lt;/span&gt; var joined = ids.Join(valueMap, id =&amp;gt; id, arr =&amp;gt; arr[0], (id, arr) =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;.Format(&lt;span style="color: #006080"&gt;&amp;quot;id: {0} - value: {1}&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;,  id, arr[1])); &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Really convenient! Let’s look at the output:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style="border-bottom: silver 1px solid; text-align: left; border-left: silver 1px solid; padding-bottom: 4px; line-height: 12pt; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding-left: 4px; width: 97.5%; padding-right: 4px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; max-height: 200px; font-size: 8pt; overflow: auto; border-top: silver 1px solid; cursor: text; border-right: silver 1px solid; padding-top: 4px" id="codeSnippetWrapper"&gt;
  &lt;div style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px" id="codeSnippet"&gt;
    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: white; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum1"&gt;   1:&lt;/span&gt; Console.WriteLine(&lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;.Join(&lt;span style="color: #006080"&gt;&amp;quot;\r\n&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;, joined)); &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;

    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum2"&gt;   2:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#160; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;

    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: white; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum3"&gt;   3:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #008000"&gt;// Prints:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;

    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum4"&gt;   4:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #008000"&gt;// id: 2 - value: 12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;

    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: white; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum5"&gt;   5:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #008000"&gt;// id: 5 - value: 15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;

    &lt;pre style="border-bottom-style: none; text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 12pt; border-right-style: none; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0em; padding-left: 0px; width: 100%; padding-right: 0px; font-family: &amp;#39;Courier New&amp;#39;, courier, monospace; direction: ltr; border-top-style: none; color: black; font-size: 8pt; border-left-style: none; overflow: visible; padding-top: 0px"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #606060" id="lnum6"&gt;   6:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #008000"&gt;// id: 3 - value: 13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;!--CRLF--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By the way, I use &lt;a title="FastSharp on MSDN" href="http://blogs.msdn.com/b/matt/archive/2010/08/08/fastsharp-2-0.aspx" target="_blank"&gt;FastSharp&lt;/a&gt; to write and test this kind of small code snippets &lt;img style="border-bottom-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-style: none; border-left-style: none" class="wlEmoticon wlEmoticon-winkingsmile" alt="Winking smile" src="http://shades-of-orange.com/image.axd?picture=wlEmoticon-winkingsmile.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Happy Coding,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Oliver&lt;/p&gt;</content>
